data-triple-N3.o: "1. Looking for extrasolar planets 2. Listening for signals 3. Robotic exploration of the Solar System]] Extraterrestrial life is defined as life that does not originate from Earth. It is often also referred to as alien life, or simply aliens (or space aliens, to differentiate from other definitions of alien or aliens). These hypothetical forms of life range from simple bacteria-like organisms to beings far more complex than humans."@en
